      "options": {
        "code": { "language": "plaintext", "showLineNumbers": false, "showMiniMap": false },
        "content": "**Example uptime** (infra only — not `sevo_*`). Alloy blackbox probes run every 30s.\n\n1. Start LGTM: `docker compose -f docker-compose.observability.yml up -d`\n2. Start the bot: `docker compose up`\n\n`grafana` probes the LGTM container. Chat/Rasa targets use the shared Docker network **`handsforbots-example`** (`t4b-webserver`, `t4b-bot`, …). **Probe duration** with **DOWN** usually means the target returned non-2xx or was unreachable — not that scraping failed.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "Hands for Bots example — uptime",
      "type": "text"
    },
